  <entry>
    <title>小试牛刀-论搭建个人博客</title>
    <link href="/polar-easterlies/polar-easterlies.github.io.git/2024/07/13/%E5%B0%8F%E8%AF%95%E7%89%9B%E5%88%80-%E8%AE%BA%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/"/>
    <url>/polar-easterlies/polar-easterlies.github.io.git/2024/07/13/%E5%B0%8F%E8%AF%95%E7%89%9B%E5%88%80-%E8%AE%BA%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1>前言</h1><p>相信很多计算机专业和非计算机专业的小伙伴使用各种平台（比如CSDN、知乎、公众号、简书等等）写过自己的技术博客，但看到那么多大佬的个性化博客，其实心里一定早就跃跃欲试搭建一个自己的博客吧。希望下面的内容能对你有所帮助，才疏学浅如有疑问或建议请评论留言，感谢支持！</p><h1>教程</h1><h2 id="1-安装node">1.安装node</h2><p>官网指路：<a href="https://nodejs.org/en/download/package-manager"></a><br>windows:以管理员身份打开powershell</p><figure class="highlight powershell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs powershell"><span class="hljs-comment"># installs fnm (Fast Node Manager)</span><br>winget install Schniz.fnm<br><br><span class="hljs-comment"># download and install Node.js</span><br>fnm use <span class="hljs-literal">--install-if-missing</span> <span class="hljs-number">20</span><br><br><span class="hljs-comment"># verifies the right Node.js version is in the environment</span><br>node <span class="hljs-literal">-v</span> <span class="hljs-comment"># should print `v20.15.0`</span><br><br><span class="hljs-comment"># verifies the right NPM version is in the environment</span><br>npm <span class="hljs-literal">-v</span> <span class="hljs-comment"># should print `10.7.0`</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>第二个命令行出错修改为</p><figure class="highlight powershell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs powershell">fnm install <span class="hljs-number">22</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>第三个命令行出错先重复上面的命令找到installation文件夹所在位置打开cmd再输入命令</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><figcaption><span>-v</span></figcaption><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs powershellnode">node -v<br>npm -v<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="2-安装hexo">2.安装hexo</h2><p>新建一个名为blog的文件夹，并在文件夹下打开GitBash输入命令</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><figcaption><span>-v</span></figcaption><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs powershellnode">npm install -g hexo-cli<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>检查是否安装成功</p><figure class="highlight powershell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs powershell">hexo <span class="hljs-literal">-v</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="3-链接github">3.链接github</h2><p>在&quot;E:\blog\myblog_config.yml”文件中修改</p><figure class="highlight powershell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs powershell">language: zn<span class="hljs-literal">-CN</span><br><br>post_asset_folder: true   <span class="hljs-comment">#改成true后在生成新文章后既有md文件也有文件夹比较清楚</span><br><br>theme: fluid         <span class="hljs-comment">#选择性修改，这里使用fluid主题，需要重新创建一个_config.fluid.yml文件将_config.yml文件中的内容复制进去，之后的细节风格修改均在_config.fluid.yml中实现</span><br><br>deploy:<br>  <span class="hljs-built_in">type</span>: git<br>  repo: ssh地址(见github)<br>  branch: master<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>GitBash中输入如下命令</p><figure class="highlight powershell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs powershell">hexo deploy<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>发现报错</p><figure class="highlight powershell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs powershell">FATAL Something<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;s wrong. Maybe you can find the solution here: https://hexo.io/docs/troubleshooting.html</span><br><span class="hljs-string">Error: Spawn failed</span><br><span class="hljs-string">    at ChildProcess.&lt;anonymous&gt; (E:\blog\myblog\node_modules\hexo-deployer-git\node_modules\hexo-util\lib\spawn.js:51:21)</span><br><span class="hljs-string">    at ChildProcess.emit (node:events:520:28)</span><br><span class="hljs-string">    at cp.emit (E:\blog\myblog\node_modules\cross-spawn\lib\enoent.js:34:29)</span><br><span class="hljs-string">    at ChildProcess._handle.onexit (node:internal/child_process:294:12)</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>检查链接状态</p><figure class="highlight powershell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs powershell">ssh <span class="hljs-literal">-vT</span> git@github.com<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight powershell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs powershell">OpenSSH_9.<span class="hljs-number">6</span>p1, OpenSSL <span class="hljs-number">3.2</span>.<span class="hljs-number">1</span> <span class="hljs-number">30</span> Jan <span class="hljs-number">2024</span><br>debug1: Reading configuration <span class="hljs-keyword">data</span> /etc/ssh/ssh_config<br>debug1: Connecting to github.com [<span class="hljs-number">127.0</span><span class="hljs-type">.0.1</span>] port <span class="hljs-number">22</span>.<br>debug1: connect to address <span class="hljs-number">127.0</span>.<span class="hljs-number">0.1</span> port <span class="hljs-number">22</span>: Connection refused<br>ssh: connect to host github.com port <span class="hljs-number">22</span>: Connection refused<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>改进修改hosts文件先将&quot;C:\Windows\System32\drivers\etc\hosts”中文件复制到桌面，使用记事本打开修改</p><figure class="highlight powershell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs powershell"><span class="hljs-comment">#127.0.0.1       localhost</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">#::1             localhost</span><br><span class="hljs-comment"># github</span><br><span class="hljs-number">140.82</span>.<span class="hljs-number">113.4</span> github.com<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>再次检查</p><figure class="highlight powershell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs powershell">ssh <span class="hljs-literal">-vT</span> git@github.com<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>发现链接成功</p><figure class="highlight powershell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs powershell">debug1: channel <span class="hljs-number">0</span>: free: client<span class="hljs-literal">-session</span>, nchannels <span class="hljs-number">1</span><br>Transferred: sent <span class="hljs-number">3160</span>, received <span class="hljs-number">2976</span> bytes, <span class="hljs-keyword">in</span> <span class="hljs-number">0.8</span> seconds<br>Bytes per second: sent <span class="hljs-number">3768.6</span>, received <span class="hljs-number">3549.1</span><br>debug1: <span class="hljs-keyword">Exit</span> status <span class="hljs-number">1</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><details open><summary><span class="pre-summary">&nbsp;</span><strong>点击查看隐藏内容</strong></summary><h2 id="Extra">Extra</h2><figure class="highlight powershell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs powershell">hexo new post 文章标题    <span class="hljs-comment">#新建文章</span><br>hexo g <span class="hljs-literal">-d</span>                <span class="hljs-comment">#推送文章</span><br>hexo s                   <span class="hljs-comment">#查看网站    Ctrl+C退出</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure></details><p>完结撒花！如有疑问请评论留言或小小支持下！</p><h1>参考</h1><p><a href="https://blog.csdn.net/ExcellentChaya/article/details/139520894">https://blog.csdn.net/ExcellentChaya/article/details/139520894</a><br><a href="https://blog.csdn.net/pijiguai/article/details/122353357">https://blog.csdn.net/pijiguai/article/details/122353357</a><br><a href="https://blog.csdn.net/weixin_41256398/article/details/117994899">https://blog.csdn.net/weixin_41256398/article/details/117994899</a><br><a href="https://blog.csdn.net/qq_59039063/article/details/132459418">https://blog.csdn.net/qq_59039063/article/details/132459418</a></p>]]></content>
    
    
    
