  <entry>
    <title>论进度条的多种姿势</title>
    <link href="/polar-easterlies/polar-easterlies.github.io.git/2024/07/12/%E8%AE%BA%E8%BF%9B%E5%BA%A6%E6%9D%A1%E7%9A%84%E5%A4%9A%E7%A7%8D%E5%A7%BF%E5%8A%BF/"/>
    <url>/polar-easterlies/polar-easterlies.github.io.git/2024/07/12/%E8%AE%BA%E8%BF%9B%E5%BA%A6%E6%9D%A1%E7%9A%84%E5%A4%9A%E7%A7%8D%E5%A7%BF%E5%8A%BF/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>#前言#<br>很多任务处理时间较长，想观察任务运行状况时需要用到进度条</p><h1>青铜段位#</h1><p>使用print函数多行输出，在小样本时效果比较清晰，然而一旦数据过大，会浪费很多内存</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs python">X = <span class="hljs-number">10000</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">for</span> i <span class="hljs-keyword">in</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">range</span>(X):<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span> j <span class="hljs-keyword">in</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">range</span>(X):<br>        k=j*i<br>        <span class="hljs-built_in">print</span>(k)<br><span class="hljs-built_in">print</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;\n完成！&quot;</span>)<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>改进</strong><br>可以尝试将情况写在同一行</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs python">X = <span class="hljs-number">10000</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">for</span> i <span class="hljs-keyword">in</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">range</span>(X):<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span> j <span class="hljs-keyword">in</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">range</span>(X):<br>        k=j*i<br>        <span class="hljs-built_in">print</span>(<span class="hljs-string">f&quot;<span class="hljs-subst">&#123;i+<span class="hljs-number">1</span>&#125;</span>/<span class="hljs-subst">&#123;X&#125;</span>&quot;</span>,end=<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;\r&#x27;</span>)<br><span class="hljs-built_in">print</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;\n完成！&quot;</span>)<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1>黄金段位#</h1><p><strong>加强</strong><br>手搓进度条</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs python">X = <span class="hljs-number">10000</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">for</span> i <span class="hljs-keyword">in</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">range</span>(X):<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span> j <span class="hljs-keyword">in</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">range</span>(X):<br>        k=j*i<br>    <span class="hljs-built_in">print</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;进度&#x27;</span>,<span class="hljs-string">f&#x27;|<span class="hljs-subst">&#123;<span class="hljs-string">&quot;*&quot;</span>*((i+<span class="hljs-number">1</span>)*<span class="hljs-number">50</span>//X):<span class="hljs-number">50</span>&#125;</span>|&#x27;</span>,<br>    <span class="hljs-string">f&#x27;<span class="hljs-subst">&#123;(i+<span class="hljs-number">1</span>)*<span class="hljs-number">100</span>//X&#125;</span>%&#x27;</span>,<br>    end=<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;\r&#x27;</span>)<br><span class="hljs-built_in">print</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;\n完成！&quot;</span>)<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1>钻石段位#</h1><p><strong>使用三方库</strong><br>progress库</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs python"><span class="hljs-keyword">from</span> progress bar <span class="hljs-keyword">import</span> Bar<br>X = <span class="hljs-number">10000</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">with</span> Bar(<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;进度&#x27;</span>,<span class="hljs-built_in">max</span>=X) <span class="hljs-keyword">as</span> bar:<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span> i <span class="hljs-keyword">in</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">range</span>(X):<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span> j <span class="hljs-keyword">in</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">range</span>(X):<br>            k=j*i<br>        bar.<span class="hljs-built_in">next</span>()<br><span class="hljs-built_in">print</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;\n完成！&quot;</span>)<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs python"><span class="hljs-keyword">from</span> progress bar <span class="hljs-keyword">import</span> Bar<br>X = <span class="hljs-number">10000</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">with</span> Bar(<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;剩余时长&#x27;</span>,<span class="hljs-built_in">max</span>=X,fill=<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;❀&#x27;</span>,<br>suffix=<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;%(percent).1f%%-%(eta)ds&#x27;</span>) <span class="hljs-keyword">as</span> bar:<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span> i <span class="hljs-keyword">in</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">range</span>(X):<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span> j <span class="hljs-keyword">in</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">range</span>(X):<br>            k=j*i<br>        bar.<span class="hljs-built_in">next</span>()<br><span class="hljs-built_in">print</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;\n完成！&quot;</span>)<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>tqdm库</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs python"><span class="hljs-keyword">from</span> tqdm <span class="hljs-keyword">import</span> tqdm<br>X = <span class="hljs-number">10000</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">for</span> i <span class="hljs-keyword">in</span> tqdm(<span class="hljs-built_in">range</span>(X)):<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span> j <span class="hljs-keyword">in</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">range</span>(X):<br>        k=j*i<br><span class="hljs-built_in">print</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;\n完成！&quot;</span>)<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs python"><span class="hljs-keyword">from</span> tqdm(.rich/.notebook/.tk) <span class="hljs-keyword">import</span> trange<br>X = <span class="hljs-number">10000</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">for</span> i <span class="hljs-keyword">in</span> trange(<span class="hljs-built_in">range</span>(X)):<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span> j <span class="hljs-keyword">in</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">range</span>(X):<br>        k=j*i<br><span class="hljs-built_in">print</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;\n完成！&quot;</span>)<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>alive-progress库</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs python"><span class="hljs-keyword">from</span> alive_progress.styles <span class="hljs-keyword">import</span> showtime<br>showtime()<br>X = <span class="hljs-number">10000</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">for</span> i <span class="hljs-keyword">in</span> tqdm(<span class="hljs-built_in">range</span>(X)):<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span> j <span class="hljs-keyword">in</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">range</span>(X):<br>        k=j*i<br><span class="hljs-built_in">print</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;\n完成！&quot;</span>)<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
    
    
